      <h1 class='title'>Ofsted</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c83WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_83ws' title='Col. 83WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c83WS' name='column_83ws' href='#column_83ws' rel='bookmark'>83WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05061'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_417'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-nick-gibb' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_417' title='Link to this speech by Mr Nick Gibb' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-nick-gibb" title="Mr Nick Gibb">Mr. Gibb</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05061">To ask the Secretary of State for Education and Skills how many Ofsted inspectors are qualified teacher trainers; and if he will make a statement. [134193]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05062'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_418'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-miliband' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_418' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Miliband' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-miliband" title="Mr David Miliband">Mr. Miliband</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05062">This is a matter for Ofsted. HM Chief Inspector, David Bell, will write to the hon. Member and place a copy of his letter in the Library.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
